data.description: Charming corner lot home in quiet East Boca Raton's Cedar Ridge idyllic neighborhood with tree lined streets and sidewalks. Great open floor plan boasting vaulted ceilings throughout, generous living and dining room, large family room, spacious eat-in kitchen with skylight.  Primary suite with walk in closet.  Much desired split bedroom floorplan.  Impact doors and windows. Huge screened patio perfect for added outdoor living space and entertaining.  This home is surrounded with front, side and backyard space with unlimited potential for a pool, summer kitchen, play area or boat storage. NO HOA.  Close to schools, Publix, restaurants and shopping. A short drive to I95 and Boca's best beaches.  Oversized 2CG with extra storage.  Great opportunity for investor to update and rent or sell.
